[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.0,
    "text": "Pearl, I finished my cold fusion generator!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.0,
    "endTime": 6.0,
    "text": "With this, we can power the entire planet! No time for that!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.0,
    "endTime": 7.0,
    "text": "Get a load of this!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.0,
    "endTime": 11.0,
    "text": "Tell her, Bobs, tell her!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.0,
    "endTime": 16.0,
    "text": "Penguin Pete started global warming to sell more ice cream! There's no way that's true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.0,
    "endTime": 18.0,
    "text": "Where are you reading this nonsense?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.0,
    "endTime": 19.0,
    "text": "The Townsville Muck Bucket."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 23.0,
    "text": "It's the news you can use that gets all the views. I don't think..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.0,
    "endTime": 25.0,
    "text": "So you better not snooze."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.0,
    "endTime": 27.0,
    "text": "Hmm, that's a long slogan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.0,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "They print the news that others are afraid to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.0,
    "endTime": 33.0,
    "text": "Like this. Tiny mayor found under mayor's hat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.0,
    "endTime": 36.0,
    "text": "Whoa, mind blown."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.0,
    "endTime": 39.0,
    "text": "Poo-wah. What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.0,
    "endTime": 41.0,
    "text": "Come on, no way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.0,
    "endTime": 44.0,
    "text": "Blossom, it's on the internet, so you know it's gotta be true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.0,
    "endTime": 45.0,
    "text": "Look at this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 53.0,
    "text": "The majority of home accidents are caused by dangerous hair bows. Ah, that's ridiculous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "Ow, my eye."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.0,
    "endTime": 58.0,
    "text": "Oh no, it's true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 62.0,
    "text": "And if you think that's bad, I got something worse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.0,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "Mojo plans to cook kittens?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.0,
    "endTime": 73.0,
    "text": "Kittens are for cuddling, not cooking. Kitties for dinner, kitties for dinner."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.0,
    "endTime": 76.0,
    "text": "They're much slimmer than full-grown cats."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.0,
    "endTime": 79.0,
    "text": "Oh, yummy, so tasty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.0,
    "endTime": 86.0,
    "text": "Your kitty cooking days are over, Mojo Jojo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.0,
    "endTime": 92.0,
    "text": "Ha ha ha ha, you will never stop me. Wait, cooking kitties?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.0,
    "endTime": 94.0,
    "text": "Oh ho ho ho, you misunderstand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.0,
    "endTime": 100.0,
    "text": "That monkey will never learn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 104.0,
    "text": "Mojo is so broken."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.0,
    "endTime": 112.0,
    "text": "Good thing we read the news, or he wouldn't have been able to save those cats. If we wanted to save those cats, shouldn't we have taken them with us?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.0,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "Okay, who just ordered a knuckle sandwich? Me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.0,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "Down with the Powerpuff Girls!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.0,
    "endTime": 124.0,
    "text": "Oh, don't play dumb."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.0,
    "endTime": 129.0,
    "text": "The muck bucket says that Bubbles puts little hamsters in jail. It's not true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.0,
    "endTime": 131.0,
    "text": "It's called a cage."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.0,
    "endTime": 133.0,
    "text": "Ha ha ha ha."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.0,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "Bubbles wouldn't do anything like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.0,
    "endTime": 144.0,
    "text": "A likely story, coming from someone who doesn't wash their hands after using the bathroom. Not even after she poured a poopy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 147.0,
    "text": "Oh no, she didn't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.0,
    "endTime": 148.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.0,
    "endTime": 152.0,
    "text": "Ha ha ha ha ha, poured a poopy, classic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.0,
    "endTime": 156.0,
    "text": "Okay, what else you guys got on my dorky sisters? Buttercup wears a toupee?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.0,
    "endTime": 158.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.0,
    "endTime": 160.0,
    "text": "Lies, lies, and slander."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.0,
    "endTime": 164.0,
    "text": "It's from the internet, so you know it's true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.0,
    "endTime": 165.0,
    "text": "Touché."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.0,
    "endTime": 168.0,
    "text": "Let's get him! Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.0,
    "endTime": 170.0,
    "text": "Right, look at the time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.0,
    "endTime": 172.0,
    "text": "It's, uh, we have a thing to..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.0,
    "endTime": 183.0,
    "text": "Go, go, go! Guys, are cages really hamster jails?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.0,
    "endTime": 185.0,
    "text": "I don't wear a toupee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.0,
    "endTime": 187.0,
    "text": "This is home-spun silk here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.0,
    "endTime": 190.0,
    "text": "I can't believe they said I don't wash my hands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.0,
    "endTime": 197.0,
    "text": "Seriously, these are the definition of clean. Whoa, I'm slipping!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.0,
    "endTime": 200.0,
    "text": " And yes, I memorized the definition of clean."
  }
]